en_160410_0	A fire has erupted in Alugolla Forest Reserve in Badulla yesterday.
en_160410_1	Police said that the fire could be put down before it spreaded to the underground drug store located nearby in the area.
en_160410_2	According to our correspondent, army, villagers and police has together put down the fire.
en_160410_3	Police suspects that animal hunters may have put up the fire in the reserve.
